":"اَسۡلَمۡنَا"},{"b":"11.6","h":"17.44","c":"وَلَمَّا","d":"walammā","e":"and has not yet","i":"وَلَمَّا"},{"b":"13.4","h":"19.72","c":"يَدۡخُلِ","d":"yadkhuli","e":"entered","i":"يَدۡخُلِ"},{"b":"14.3","h":"21.1","c":"ٱلۡإِيمَٰنُ","d":"l-īmānu","e":"the faith","i":"الۡاِيۡمَانُ"},{"b":"15.5","h":"23.16","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِىۡ"},{"b":"15.9","h":"23.91","c":"قُلُوبِكُمۡۖ","d":"qulūbikum","e":"your hearts","i":"قُلُوۡبِكُمۡۚ"},{"b":"17.8","h":"29.45","c":"وَإِن","d":"wa-in","e":"But if","i":"وَاِنۡ"},{"b":"19.3","h":"30.64","c":"تُطِيعُواْ","d":"tuṭīʿū","e":"you obey","i":"تُطِيۡعُوا"},{"b":"20.2","h":"32.28","c":"ٱللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهَ"},{"b":"21.0","h":"33.75","c":"وَرَسُولَهُۥ","d":"warasūlahu","e":"and His Messenger","i":"وَرَسُوۡلَهٗ"},{"b":"22.6","h":"36.26","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"not","i":"لَا"},{"b":"22.9","h":"36.98","c":"يَلِتۡكُم","d":"yalit'kum","e":"He will deprive you","i":"يَلِتۡكُمۡ"},{"b":"24.7","h":"39.11","c":"مِّنۡ","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِّنۡ"},{"b":"25.2","h":"39.91","c":"أَعۡمَٰلِكُمۡ","d":"aʿmālikum","e":"your deeds","i":"اَعۡمَالِكُمۡ"},{"b":"26.","h":"42.42","c":"شَيۡـًٔاۚ","d":"shayan","e":"anything","i":"شَيۡـًٔــاؕ"},{"b":"28.1","h":"42.93","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"Indeed","i":"اِنَّ"},{"b":"29.5","h":"47.46","c":"ٱللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهَ"},{"b":"30.","h":"48.87","c":"غَفُورٞ","d":"ghafūrun","e":"(is) Oft-Forgiving","i":"غَفُوۡرٌ"},{"b":"31.6","h":"51.07","c":"رَّحِيمٌ","d":"raḥīmun","e":"Most Merciful","i":"رَّحِيۡمٌ"}],"a":{"g":"The bedouins say, \"We have believed.\" Say, \"You have not [yet] believed; but say [instead], 'We have submitted,' for faith has not yet entered your hearts. And if you obey Allah and His Messenger, He will not deprive you from your deeds of anything. Indeed, Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.\""}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"1.15","c":"إِنَّمَا","d":"innamā","e":"Only","i":"اِنَّمَا"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.67","c":"ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنُونَ","d":"l-mu'minūna","